00:00:00,170 --> 00:00:02,280
Can users of SNORT write rules?

2
00:00:02,280 --> 00:00:03,030
Yes.

3
00:00:03,030 --> 00:00:06,770
Can the community who maintains
a large set of SNORT rules?

4
00:00:06,770 --> 00:00:08,050
Of course.

5
00:00:08,050 --> 00:00:10,930
Can the security experts write rules?

6
00:00:10,930 --> 00:00:12,140
Of course.

7
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:16,379
As an open source software,
everyone can write rules for SNORT.

8
00:00:16,379 --> 00:00:20,320
The rules can then be submitted and
improved by security experts, and

9
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,340
shared with the community.
